biography: Thorben Jensen has studied, designed and automated predictive models since many years. After studies in 5 countries, he graduated from the PhD program at Delft University of Technology. His [PhD thesis](http://pure.tudelft.nl/ws/files/12909024/Jensen_dissertation_2_.pdf) proposes and explores increased use of automation when building models with autonomous agents. On this topic, he has previously spoken on international conferences and published peer-reviewed literature, e.g. [here](https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1364815216303814).
